Mongrethod Starting stats 4 Int, 3 Agi, 9 Str, base speed 320, base damage 6, Stats Gain per level 0.70 int, 1.30 str, 0.40 agi
Starting item Gaint Cleaver give 7 damage and 4% lifesteal base attack time 2.20 Auto-Attack,Tank,Mage

LEVEL 20 TALENT

Talent 1
5 armor 250 life and 7% magic resist

Talent 2
25 damage -15 attack speed and 10% spell amp

PASSIVE D OR F PitLord
Increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF Mongrethod will gain 2 life per intelligence points and he gets 10% damage reduction he also increase is strenght
by 15% of is intelligence he also start with a Special Ring Item that scale with evert level. he can have 2 other Ring with this one
DEBUFF Mongrethod lose 90 attack speed and lose 50% of mana and he take 180% more damage from pure type,he cannot pass 350 basespeed and
he cannot use any-other weapons but Cleaver

UnderWorld Ring Special Item
increase spell amp by 2% increase by 0.2% every level
increase mana regeneration by 1 increase by 0.2 every level
increase life regeneration by 0.5 increase by 0.1 every level
can also be use to double the effect of the Ring for 10 second, cooldown of 80 second

talent level 25 upgrade PitLord
add a new modifier Chaos Lord
Mongrethod gain 30% spell amp with 10% armor increase he also gain 6% cooldown reduction and he now summon a permanent chaos Infernal
that got 80% of life and 100% damage of Mongrethod respawn every 20 second up to 2 max if they die, they will respawn after 20 second


SPELL Q Rain of Fire
Channel a raining wave of fire from the sky dealing damage and burn the enemy for a % of max health and current health for bosses
it also reduce the enemy movement speed every time they get damage by Rain of Fire

damage 4 9 13 17 plus 20% of strenght per wave, damage type pure
burn damage 0.2% 0.3% 0.4% 0.5% of max Health, damage type magical per second
burn damage 0.2% 0.3% 0.4% 0.5% of current Health, damage type magical per second for bosses
amount of waves 3 4 5 6
duration of channel 3 4 5 6
duration of burn damage and slow 2 second
movement speed lost per damage 2% 3% 4% 5%
radius 200 240 280 320
radius increase by 1 for every point of strenght
cooldown 20
manacost 100 115 130 145 plus 2% of max mana

talent level 10 Upgrade Rain of Fire
Increase strenght scaling by 30%
increase current life as damage by 0.2%
reduce cooldown by 6
reduce mana cost by 40
no longer a channel

add a new modifier Rain of Chaos
every wave of Rain of fire will summon a Chaos Infernal, this summon will have 35% life,50% damage of Mongrethod
they also have 2 armor and 5% magicresist this bonus increase by 1 armor and 2% magic resist every 10 level of Mongrethod
they last 12 second up to 6 max


